Package edu.acase.hvz.hvz_app

The root package for this app

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BaseActivity
    Base class for all activities
    BasePlayerActivity<ReportModel extends BaseReportModel>
    Base class for all player views.
    CommonDialogs
    The common dialogs between the player activities.
    HumanActivity
    The activity for human players.
    IncubatingActivity
    Incubating is the state that humans are in once they have been tagged by a zombie player.
    Logger
    This is a utility class for activities or other files to use to log messages to Logcat instead of using stdout/stderr.
    MapMarker
    A map marker is the object used to connect markers to reports.
    MoveMarker
    This is the activity that players are shown whenever they want to move a marker that is already on the map.
    StunnedActivity
    Stunned is the state that zombies are in once they have been tagged by a human player.
    ViewCode
    This activity shows the human player their code so that they can reveal it to zombies whenever they are tagged.
    ZombieActivity
    The activity for zombie players.
